text: Kupoyarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Alginsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 15 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Davlekanovo, 3 km from Alga. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kupoyarovo
